data.description: Introducing a stunning three-bedroom, two-bathroom pool house nestled in the heart of Port Saint Lucie, Florida. This exceptional residence boasts a sprawling lot spanning over 15,000 square feet, providing ample space for outdoor activities and landscaping enthusiasts. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal environment for both entertaining and everyday living. Featuring a double car garage, jacuzzi, new shed this home conveys a list of extras. (2018 AC and recently installed roof.)
